overview: Motörhead's 10th anniversary show at the Hammersmith Odeon in London, England on 26 June 1985. ----Setlist----  1. Iron Fist  2. Stay Clean  3. The Hammer  4. Metropolis  5. Mean Machine  6. On the Road  7. Killed by Death  8. Ace of Spades  9. Steal Your Face  10. Nothing Up My Sleeve  11. (We Are) The Road Crew  12. Bite the Bullet  13. title: Motörhead: The Birthday Party
